com.ami.mse.ucms.templates

Class TemplateBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ami.mse.ucms.templates.TemplateBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Named(value="templateBean")
@ViewAccessScoped
public class TemplateBean
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Contains methods for save the instance of Template and method that generate HTML components for the page upload-document according to selected template from the SelectOneMenu in the same page.

    Tony

    • Method Detail

      • save

        public String save()
        Saves the instance of the Template. Uses the FacesContext to get the list of the components that the user is generate. Sets the message when the save is successful or fails. Fails when there is template with the same name.
        Returns:
        the string

      • extractTemplate

        public String extractTemplate()
        Generate the fields of the selected template from the SelectOneMenu in the page upload-documents. First finds the JavaServer Faces form in which will generate components for the template. Next finds components for the selected template and generate them according to their type. Those component are added in List of UIComponent that is iterated at the end of the method to put the components plus their labels in to the found form.
        Returns:
        the string

      • findTemplates

        public List<com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.template.Template> findTemplates()
        Finds all records for Template from the data base and return them in list of templates.
        Returns:
        list of found templates or null if there are none records of templates in the data base

      • findApprovedTemplates

        public List<com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.template.Template> findApprovedTemplates()
        Finds all records for Template that are approved from the data base and return them in list of templates.
        Returns:
        list of found templates which are approved or null if there are none records of templates in the data base

      • transformTemplateApproval

        public String transformTemplateApproval(boolean approved)
        Transform boolean value to string. Used to transform the approved status for templates in approve-template page.
        Parameters:
        approved - the status of the template that will be transform
        Returns:
        string representation of approval status for the template

      • viewTemplateDetails

        public void viewTemplateDetails(com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.template.Template template)

      • approveTempalte

        public void approveTempalte(com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.template.Template template)
        Changes the approval status of the given Template. If it's true change it to false and opposite. Sets the approval status for the template and update it in the data base.
        Parameters:
        template - the given template on which will be changed approval status

      • refreshCurrentPage

        public void refreshCurrentPage()
        Force redirect to the approve-template page or view-templates. This redirect depends on that if the logged user has role administrator or not, if he has it will redirect to approve-template. Gets external context and makes request for redirect.
        Throws:
        IOException - when the approved-template or view-templates pages missing for some reason
